    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a superlative 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera 4S (996.2) finished in Arctic Silver over Black full leather. This wide-body example features the M96.03 3.6L flat-six, benefiting from a documented LN Engineering IMS bearing retrofit and a recently replaced Rear Main Seal (RMS). The G96 6-speed manual transaxle exhibits precise gate transitions with no synchro hesitation, feeding power through the factory viscous-clutch AWD system. The chassis dynamics are enhanced by a Bilstein PSS10 coilover suite, providing adjustable damping and optimized roll centers. Engine health is confirmed by consistent Blackstone oil reports and a recent compression test showing variance within 2% across all cylinders. Every vacuum line, bushing, and coolant expansion tank has been refreshed to ensure peak thermal efficiency and structural rigidity. This is a turn-key, investment-grade driver for the meticulous collector.",
      "price": 46500.0,
